# Sales Performance Analysis Dashboard

## Project Overview
This Power BI project analyzes sales performance, customer insights, and product profitability using transactional sales data.

## Tools Used
- Power BI
- Excel
- DAX
- Data Modeling

## Dashboard Pages
### Executive Overview
Provides insights into revenue, profit, profit margin, customer count, and sales trends.

### Customer Insights
Analyzes customer demographics, retention, customer segments, and revenue distribution.

### Product Profitability
Evaluates product performance, category profitability, and top-performing products.

## Key Findings
- Total Revenue: 40.62M
- Total Profit: 13.09M
- Profit Margin: 32.2%
- West region generated the highest revenue.
- Office Supplies was the best-performing category.
- Consumer customers generated the highest revenue.

